{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-remark-vega","description":"Adds the ability to include a [Vega](https://vega.github.io/vega/) visualization from a markdown file.","keywords":["vega","gatsby-transform-remark","gatsby","gatsby-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"thekevinscott","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/11f28715493c9556dd7a4ffca767ede3"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/thekevinscott/gatsby-remark-vega"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-remark-vega\"><a href=\"#gatsby-remark-vega\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-remark-vega</h1>\n<p>Adds the ability to include a <a href=\"https://vega.github.io/vega/\">Vega</a> visualization from a markdown file.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thekevinscott/gatsby-remark-vega/master/chart.png\" alt=\"An example of an embedded Vega visualization\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<p>In your markdown, you can include <code class=\"language-text\">vega</code> JSON files like so:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">My awesome post needs a chart:\n\n`vega:chart.json`\n\nLook at that chart!</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>The json file should sit within the same folder as the markdown file.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/thekevinscott/gatsby-remark-vega-example\">An example repo demonstrating the plugin is available</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"installation\"><a href=\"#installation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<p>The plugin can be installed with <code class=\"language-text\">npm</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code>:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install gatsby-transformer-remark rehype-react gatsby-remark-vega</code></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add gatsby-transformer-remark rehype-react gatsby-remark-vega</code></p>\n<p>The process for installing this plugin mimics that of <a href=\"https://github.com/hebilicious/gatsby-remark-component\"><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-remark-component</code></a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"1\"><a href=\"#1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.</h3>\n<p>Include the plugin in <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>, as a plugin option for <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-transformer-remark</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// In your gatsby-config.js\nplugins: [\n  {\n    resolve: `gatsby-transformer-remark`,\n    options: {\n      plugins: [\n        `gatsby-remark-vega`,\n      ],\n    },\n  },\n];</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h3 id=\"2\"><a href=\"#2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.</h3>\n<p>In your template, follow the same technique as showcased in <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-remark-component</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// within your markdown template\nimport rehypeReact from &quot;rehype-react&quot;\nimport Vega, { KEY as VegaKey } from &quot;gatsby-remark-vega/dist/client&quot;;\n\nconst renderAst = new rehypeReact({\n  createElement: React.createElement,\n  components: {\n    [vegaKey]: Vega,\n  }\n}).Compiler</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h3 id=\"3\"><a href=\"#3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3.</h3>\n<p>Where you render your markdown, replace:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: post.html }} /&gt;</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>with</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div&gt;{renderAst(post.htmlAst)}&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h3 id=\"4\"><a href=\"#4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4.</h3>\n<p>In your graphql query, make sure to select <code class=\"language-text\">htmlAst</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">...\nmarkdownRemark(fields: { slug: { eq: $slug } }) {\n htmlAst // previously `html`\n ...\n}</code></pre>\n      </div>","timeToRead":2}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-remark-vega/","id":"3b14606d-4105-5148-af57-10228f86ef24"}}